- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper may involve the use of cameras or other sensors for perception and obstacle detection. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper may involve the use of machine learning or other AI techniques for decision-making. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also possible as the paper may involve the use of learning algorithms for path planning or obstacle avoidance. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with control of a complex system (autonomous bus) in a dynamic environment.
